      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To establish a commission to study the relocation of select executive agencies or divisions of such agencies outside the Washington metropolitan area, to make recommendations to Congress on appropriate findings, and for other purposes.</title>
